      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "Reason :\n\n<b> THEY SHOW STATISTICAL INDEPENDENCE. AS THEIR PEARSON AND SPEARMAN COEFFICIENTS ARE < 0.7 . </b>\n<hr>",
